Customer: Hello?

Executive: Yes.

Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji. Abhi meri aawaz aa rahi hai na?
Executive: Haan, aa rahi hai. Accha.
Executive: Sorry madam, aapka aawaz nahi aa raha hai. Abhi boliye.
Customer: Main bol rahi hu ki jaise mera next month expire hone wala hai.
Executive: Ji, ji.
Customer: To main is month bhi koi buylead use nahi kar sakti kya?
Executive: Use kar sakte ho na madam aap.
Customer: To matlab aap mujhe dekh ke bata sakte ho ki meri jaise is week ki kitni buyleads maine consume kar li hai. Jaise agar per week mere ko 10 buylead mil rahi hai.
Hmm, hmm. Maine kitni consume kar li hai is week mein?
Executive: Thik hai madam, main abhi batata hu. Aap system mein hai aap abhi?
Customer: Sorry?
Executive: Aap system mein hai abhi? Abhi online hai aap?
Customer: Nahi, main app mein hi hu.
Executive: Thik hai, no issues. Ah, main ek, ek minute main aapka jo ye open karta hu, account open karta hu.

Customer: Ah, aapko to enquiries hai na madam. Abhi last.
Executive: Matlab dekh rahi hu mere ko enquiries hai, wo mujhe samajh mein aa raha hai. Aur main unko contact karne ki try kar rahi hu. Jaise maine aaj subah ek jan ko contact kiya.
Executive: Thik hai, aapko to uske uske baad mein buyleads consume karta hu aapko stop ho jata hai, right?
Customer: Abhi uske baad mein payment karna karna batata hai. Nahi, main, haan, is week mein maine buyleads consume kari hi nahi hai. To main aapse puchna chah rahi hu ki kitni buyleads consume kare. Agar jaise mujhe nahi pata to aap mujhe bata sakte hai kya?
Executive: Sure madam. Madam actually aap ye ek hafte mein 17 buyleads consume kar sakte ho.
Customer: Thik hai, ek hafte mein kitni consume ho gayi hai?
Executive: Ji main batata hu. Abhi ye hafte start hua so aapko aake ah Sunday se, Sunday se yaad rakho madam. Second of November se main bolta hu. Second of November ko aapko 10, 10 leads to aapko ah allocate hua hai.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Thik. Ah, aap aake main, main aapko main batata hu, data batata hu. Just app open karke rakhiye.
Customer: Ek minute.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Thik hai, open kar liya.
Executive: Buyleads section pe aa jao.
Customer: Buyleads balance pe ya kaise?
Executive: Nahi, buyleads section mein aa jao. Wo buyleads balance hai na, wo click kar dijiye.
Customer: Buyleads section mein aa gayi.
Executive: Thik hai. Abhi right side mein top mein dekho aapko three dot button hai na madam. Three dot.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Wo click kare baad aapko buyleads balance batayega. Aur buyleads transaction batayega, hai na? Past transaction.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Past transaction. Wo click kare to aapko transaction history batata hai na?
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Hai na? Abhi aap usme calculate karo. Second of November aap totally ah

Executive: Totally nine buyleads tak consume kiye hai, right?
Customer: Nahi sir, aap khud sochiye ki main ek hi buylead pe char baar to call nahi karungi na.
Executive: Ah, ek hi buylead pe char baar, nahi madam. Aap ek ek lead bhi 10 lead same date mein liye hai. Aap dekho second of November mein ah Srikanth Sri and M. Robert and C. Janaki Raman, in Arun Kumar, Balaji, Tony and Saranya Rajesh aisa ek 10 aadmi ko aap same day mein contact kiye hai.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: To aapko 17 leads aa raha hai na? Wo 17 leads mein 60, 60% of leads same day aap consume kiye hai. And daily basis mein aapko ek ek lead aa raha hai. Wo daily leads aap consume kar rahe hai. To ye to chal raha hai.
Customer: Thik hai, samajh gayi. Thik hai.
Customer: To main yearly aapko pay karti hu to wo kis cheez ke liye payment hoti hai?
Executive: Ah, yearly payment ah samajh mein nahi aa raha hai na? Aur ek baar bataiye.
Customer: Nahi, main samajh gayi ji. Mere ko jo doubt tha wo clear.
Executive: Sorry madam, mujhe nahi samajh mein aa raha hai. Aapka voice thoda [unintelligible] aa raha hai.
Customer: Clear ho gaya. Thank you.
Executive: Madam aapko solution mil gaya?
Customer: Haan, mil gaya. Thank you.
Executive: Thik hai madam, ek, ek baat madam. Abhi main ye, ye aapka concern jo close karta hu, aapko jo ek ye milega ah feedback mail milega aapka jo mail ID pe. Wo just tumne wo feedback only de do. If my resolution is okay, you just give me a good feedback about this.
Customer: Done, done. Thank you.
Executive: That's fine na? Okay. Okay sir. Thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to know about buyleads consumption.

- Enquires about yearly payment details.



Resolution:

- Explained about buyleads consumption process.

- Clarified the number of buyleads consumed.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will send feedback mail.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, subscription, payment, enquiries
